<span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">name</span><span class="p">);</span> 			<span class="c1">// Number</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>æ³¨ï¼šä½¿ç”¨ä¸€å…ƒè¿ç®—ç¬¦ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">+</code> å¯ä»¥å®ç°å…¶ä»–ç±»å‹è½¬æ¢ä¸ºæ•°å­—ç±»å‹ã€‚</p>

<h5 id="å¸ƒå°”å‹è½¬æ¢">å¸ƒå°”å‹è½¬æ¢</h5>

<p>Boolean() å°† nullã€ç©ºå­—ç¬¦ä¸²ã€0ã€undefined å’Œ NaN è½¬ä¸º <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">false</code>ï¼Œå…¶ä»–è½¬ä¸º <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">true</code>ï¼š</p>

